quote.nm: C&D Property Management Group Co., Ltd
quote.summary: C&D Property Management Group Co Ltd is a company principally engaged in comprehensive property management and relevant value-added services. The Company operates four business sectors. Property management services provides greening, gardening and order maintenance, cleaning, parking management, repair and maintenance services. Community value-added and synergy services provides home living services, home beauty services, real estate brokerage and asset management services, value-added services for public areas, elderly-care and health value- added services and smart community services. Value-added services to non-property owners include consultancy services to property developers and other non-property owners and reception, order maintenance and cleaning services. Commercial property operation management services comprise positioning, planning and design consultancy services, provision of tenant and lease management, operation management and planning and marketing services.
